                                ##### basic user ######

 1 - should be create a class or entity  User and Role   :- relation between two classes (AppUser - Role) 
 2 - should be create a Repository and Services for two classes 
 3 - may be  create a StartUpApp for add some users for a test 
 4 - and Run the project for test  

                                ##### security ###### 

 1 - Add dependencies :-  Spring Security - JWT 
 2 - Create a Class UserDetail implements from UserDetails  
 3 - in UserService implements UserDetailsService for add loadUserByUsername -- and should be encode a password 
 4 - Create a Class TokenUtil :- for add some method like generate token and expiration date and ....... look to the project
 5 - Create a Class AuthFilter : - for filter any Api in the project by token 
 6 - Create a Class SecurityConfig :- to add all Configuration
 7 - Create a Class AuthController 
